Pick up the egg from the sofa.
take it to the sink in the bathroom.
Put the egg in the sink, wash it and then remove it.

high_descs: Turn around and leave the room and take a left into the living room and go to the right of the sofa.
Pick up the egg on the couch.
Turn around take a right and go down the hallway on the right and enter the bathroom the third door on the left.
Put the egg in the sink, turn the water on, and take the egg out.
Leave the bathroom take a right in the hallway and go into the second door on your right.
Put the egg on the sidetable.

high_descs: Exit from the bedroom turn right go to the living room sofa near to the lamp.
Take the egg from the sofa.
Turn around go straight turn right go to the bathroom sink.
Put the egg in the sink, pour water over it, clean it, and take it back.
Exit from the bathroom turn right go straight then turn right to the sidetable.
Place the egg on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Take an egg from the sofa, clean it, and place it on the side table.
